data.value: About this item 60W INCANDESCENT REPLACEMENT BULB - This LED lamp is an energy-efficient replacement and substitute for standard 60-watt incandescent lamps. At 9 watts, it emits a daylight output of 750 lumens and a temperature of 5000K. LONG-LASTING – These bulbs are a great energy-saving replacement for old bulbs because they have a total lifespan of up to 7 years. You won’t need to constantly change your lightbulbs anymore ENERGY-SAVING – These LED light bulbs require less energy and can save on your energy bill. An estimated energy cost of only Dollar-1.08 per year.
